RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_DESC, AC_GL_CCY, CUST_NO FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT WHERE /*USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND */NVL(BRANCH_CODE, ?) = ? ORDER BY CUST_NO
SELECT MIS_GROUP FROM MITMS_MIS_GROUP WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY MIS_GROUP
SELECT TRN_CODE,TRN_DESC /*,CHEQUE_MANDATORY*/ FROM OLTMS_TRN_CODE WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY TRN_CODE

SELECT PERIOD_CODE, FIN_CYCLE FROM (SELECT X.FIN_CYCLE,Y.PERIOD_CODE FROM OLTMS_FIN_CYCLE X, OLTMS_PERIOD_CODES Y WHERE X.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND X.FIN_CYCLE = Y.FIN_CYCLE AND Y.PC_END_DATE <= (SELECT MAX(B.PC_END_DATE) FROM OLTMS_BRANCH A, OLTMS_PERIOD_CODES B WHERE A.CURRENT_PERIOD = B.PERIOD_CODE AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.CURRENT_CYCLE = B.FIN_CYCLE)) WHERE 1 = 1
SELECT CUSTOMER_NO,SHORT_NAME FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND ONCE_AUTH='Y' ORDER BY CUSTOMER_NO
